-- Genentech shares soar 16.7 percent on Roche offer
-- 
-- Mon Jul 21, 2008 8:18am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/21/us-markets-stocks-beforethebell-idUSN2138950220080721

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of U.S. biotech company Genentech soared 16.7 percent to $95.50 before the bell on Monday after Swiss drugmaker Roche Holding AG offered to acquire all outstanding stocks of its partner for $43.7 billion in cash. 

 (Reporting by  Walter Brandimarte ; Editing by Theodore d'Afflisio)